contextValue.description: The value to be passed to the TabListProvider above all the tabs.

dispatch.description: Action dispatcher for the tabs list component. Allows to programmatically control the tabs list.

getRootProps.description: Resolver for the root slot's props.

highlightedValue.description: The value of the currently highlighted tab.

isRtl.description: If true, it will indicate that the text's direction in right-to-left.

selectedValue.description: The value of the currently selected tab.
